k. Milk is a high quality nutrition source, so govt. will provide nutritious milk once in a week to those children\u201d.", "009-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/dehradun/cms-scheme-to-now-provide-milk-to-school-students/articleshow/74600752.cms"}}